Hamsters are pets you can interact with instead of just observe (like fish or tarantulas), and they're just as capable of being loving and affectionate in their own little ways. My old dwarf hamster Hoshi would sit and chill on my shoulder for ages whilst I'd be on my laptop or watch TV.
